      <div class="msgContentFrame">Anyone have any advice how to get helmet crabs? <br /> <br />I would think something catchable in grade 2 would be easy to farm but its been a complete nightmare for me. With 30+ fishing I was able to get 3 of these in grade 2 outside of skull valley in an hour using a bamboo rod and lugworms. And that was only following the schools of fish (without the schools im pretty sure these are completely impossible to catch) <br /> <br />Is there ANYWAY to get these things quickly and or in bulk (or even just a better way than 3-4 an hour), even if it involves actually fishing at a higher level zone because getting them @ skull valleys a nightmare. <br /> <br />Thanks for any help or advice :D</div>
