      <div class="msgContentFrame">I used to get quite a few of these during the leve from skull with the 3 fishing spots on the cliffs, but as I ranked up I moved on to different waters. I did notice I was catching more crabs as I was gaining ranks though. You might want to try blood worms, I'm still doing rank 30 and 40 leves with blood worms, I just seem to get the best result with those on leves. Just stay in one of the spots and let the timer run out on the leve so you can catch more crabbies.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>FFXIV: Dennis Galen - FSH 37 | WEA 21 | CRP 18 | LEA 17 | CON 9 - Selbina server <br />FFXIV: Dennis Ramuh - CON 7 | ALC 7 - Selbina server <br />FFXI: Dennis - Hume Rank 10 Bastok - Ramuh server - LS: PandemoniumKnights <br /><a href="http://ffxi.allakhazam.com/profile.xml?193242" rel="external">60 Summoner</a> <br /><a href="http://ffxi.allakhazam.com/profile.xml?27938" rel="external">75 Black Mage</a> | <a href="http://ffxi.allakhazam.com/profile.xml?8902" rel="external">75 White Mage</a> <br /><a href="http://ffxi.allakhazam.com/profile.xml?178225" rel="external">75 Red Mage</a> | <a href="http://ffxi.allakhazam.com/profile.xml?85078" rel="external">AlchaFisherMage</a> <br />Alchemy 93,1 +2 | Fish 100 | Gold 32 <br />Wood 22 | Cooking 15 | Smith 14 | Leather 9</div></div>
