      <div class="msgContentFrame">There's a specific lure (<a href="HTTP://ffxiv.yg.com/item/cage-feeder?id=3940110" rel="external nofollow" title="ffxiv.yg.com/item/cage-feeder?id=3940110">Cage Feeder</a>) that might be suitable for catching helmet crabs.  If I could bring myself to mess around with fishing a bit more I'd make one and try it out but as it is, I'm not huge on fishing.  Need a rank 28+ armorer to make, but it sounds like the same principle as your standard crab trap.  Put food for the crabs in cage, drop cage to bottom, crabs go inside cage to get food, pull cage up, crabs are trapped, hurray. <br /> <br />Just a theory.</div>
